<HL>
   Ex-Consumers' Gas
   Official Plans Offer
   If Rival Bid Barred
</HL>
<DATE>
05/24/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
